{"tid":1386652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《軍事討論》勇武新方向，前線唔該入黎","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:33:23.000Z","uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16243b401173643fbbb5b748299638efa77ca5db","tid":1386652,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"家所謂既勇武，所謂既be water<br />\n直接D講只係一味死守陣地<br />\n次次都俾人圍攻 俾人當耙射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人數再多 裝備再齊 時間一拖長<br />\n最後都係敗走<br />\n殺敵零個 自損三千<br />\n有勇無謀 白白送頭<br />\n輸喺邊度?<br />\n被動 無目標 無組織 無指揮<br />\n個個各有各做 散兵遊勇<br />\n<br />\n咁應該點做?<br />\ndon't be water<br />\nBe Ice ！<br />\n線上製定好戰術 放棄守陣 主動遊擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n線下去到集合地點 即時分配成不同部隊 小隊<br />\n每次都要有 臨時指揮部 臨時指揮官<br />\n(每次唔同人 不要大台)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />指揮官負責發號施令 攻 退 守 散 轉場<br />\n所有人員根據指示作出行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(好多人根本無主見 只係跟大隊做)<br />\n行動效律會大大提升<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上只係大方向既建議<br />\n詳細戰術自有各大軍師出謀獻策<br />\n利申：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講緊打war game"},{"pid":"6e838c42b5782a7cdcfb578e5a0041418020988c","tid":1386652,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"[前線討論] 進場、攻守及退場情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386027</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n師兄入呢個post？想集中討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c85b559